### 商家优惠券管理API测试文件

### 1. 获取优惠券列表（分页）
GET http://localhost:5250/api/merchant/coupons?page=1&pageSize=10
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 获取优惠券统计信息
GET http://localhost:5250/api/merchant/coupons/stats
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. 创建满减券
POST http://localhost:5250/api/merchant/coupons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "新用户专享券",
  "type": "fixed",
  "value": 10,
  "minAmount": 50,
  "totalQuantity": 1000,
  "startTime": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "description": "新用户专享优惠券，满50减10"
}

### 4. 创建折扣券
POST http://localhost:5250/api/merchant/coupons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "会员折扣券",
  "type": "discount",
  "value": 0.8,
  "totalQuantity": 500,
  "startTime": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "description": "会员专享8折优惠券"
}

### 5. 更新优惠券（需要先创建优惠券获取ID）
PUT http://localhost:5250/api/merchant/coupons/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "更新后的优惠券名称",
  "type": "fixed",
  "value": 15,
  "minAmount": 80,
  "totalQuantity": 800,
  "startTime": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "description": "更新后的描述"
}

### 6. 删除单个优惠券
DELETE http://localhost:5250/api/merchant/coupons/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. 批量删除优惠券
DELETE http://localhost:5250/api/merchant/coupons/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

### 8. 测试错误情况 - 创建无效的满减券（优惠金额大于最低消费）
POST http://localhost:5250/api/merchant/coupons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "无效优惠券",
  "type": "fixed",
  "value": 100,
  "minAmount": 50,
  "totalQuantity": 100,
  "startTime": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "description": "这是一个无效的优惠券"
}

### 9. 测试错误情况 - 创建无效的折扣券（折扣比例不在0-1之间）
POST http://localhost:5250/api/merchant/coupons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "无效折扣券",
  "type": "discount",
  "value": 1.5,
  "totalQuantity": 100,
  "startTime": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "description": "这是一个无效的折扣券"
}
